# Enter a number and have teh comptuer tell you if it is an Odd or 
# Even number.
# Write a program that asks for two numbers and does all the math 
# things to those two numbers aka: Addition, Subtraction, multipli-
# -cation, and division.


puts "Give a value for x"
x = gets.chomp.to_f
puts "Give a value for y"
y = gets.chomp.to_f

puts "_________"
puts "Addition"
puts " "
puts (x + y)

puts "_________"
puts "Subtraction"
puts " "
puts (x - y)

puts "_________"
puts "Multiplication"
puts " "
puts (x * y)

puts "_________"
puts "Division"
puts " "
puts (x / y)